epository` 接口：\n     ```dart\n     Future<({List<ConversationItem> items, boo
l hasMore, String? nextCursor})> getConversations(...)\n     ```\n  2. `ImReposi
toryImpl` 从响应中解析 `data[\'next_cursor\']` 和 `data[\'has_more\']`；\n  3. C
ubit 中使用服务端返回的 `nextCursor`：\n     ```dart\n     nextCursor: result.ne
xtCursor,\n     hasMore: result.hasMore,\n     ```\n- **依据**: `docs/api-contra
cts/im.yaml` 中 `ListConversations` 的响应结构包含 `next_cursor` / `has_more`；P
